---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/italy-me.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="A little about me and my career journey"
	pubDate={new Date('April 2, 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>✨ professional career</h2>
	<details>
		<summary>Feb 2018 - Current: <br/>Software Engineer -> Senior Software Engineer -> Staff Engineer @ <strong>Aetna</strong></summary>
		<em>I work on Aetna member features &amp; our design system component library.</em>
	</details>
	<details>
		<summary>Sept 2017 - Jan 2018: Freelanced while traveling</summary>
		<p>Did some work for small startups &amp; the Texas State Athletic Trainers Association.</p>
	</details>
	<details>
		<summary>Oct 2015 - Aug 2017: <br/>Front-end Developer -> Senior Front-end Developer @ <strong>Kalkomey</strong></summary>
		<em>I worked on both the custom content management system and licensing system.</em>
		<ul>
			<li>Led the UI development for a customizable storefront (react/rails)</li>
			<li>Built the UI for the internal CMS/LMS. (angular2+/rails)</li>
			<li>Led the UI for the pro duct suite, “Agency Management Solution” which allows for states to manage subscriptions, licensing, tags, etc.</li>
			<li>Created code standards and living styleguides for all new projects for rapid development and consistency across products which, for example, led to a new product UI to be demo-able to clients in less than 5 weeks.</li>
		</ul>
	</details>
	<details>
		<summary>Apr 2014 - Aug 2015: Software Engineer II @ <strong>Join'em</strong> (startup)</summary>
		<p>Built the UI for a social e-commerce web app (angular1.x/Django) working closely with back-end engineers to launch the MVP. Created the living styleguide and a custom reusable pattern library.</p>
	</details>
	<details>
		<summary>Aug 2013 - Apr 2014: Front-end Developer @ <strong>Apollo Interactive</strong></summary>
		<p>Maintained and created new web pages for clients such as Wingstop, Visionworks, Stage Stores, Cache Creek, Cur ves, Extraco Banks, Studio Movie Grill, and Einstein Bros Bagels.</p>
	</details>
	<p><a href="../web-resume.pdf">resume.pdf</a></p>
	<h2>🔎 education/internships</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>2011-2013: web dev internships at design/marketing agencies</li>
		<li>2011-2013: on-campus job as graphics/web designer for RecSports dept</li>
		<li>2011-2013: Graduated from <strong>UT-Dallas</strong> w/a BA in Emerging Media &amp; Comms (focus on UX), minored in Philosophy</li>
		<li>2008-2011: Graduated from <strong>Dallas College</strong> w/an AAS in Arts &amp; Tech (essentially UX + CS)</li>
	</ul>
	<p>feel free to reach out to me via <a href="https://github.com/sceendy/sceendy.github.io/issues" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">github issues</a>; add the [public DM] label</p>
